articles.title: KL Rahul, Shreyas Iyer doubtful starters for India in Asia Cup 2023 - Hindustan Times
articles.description: If Rahul manages to recover quickly from here, he can be picked provisionally for the WC.  | Cricket
articles.content:
Indias middle-order regulars Shreyas Iyer and KL Rahul are doubtful starters for the Asia Cup that begins on August 30. Iyers participation in the World Cup, it is learned, is also uncertain.
